>\n等等等等<br />\n如果有打死人 就犯多條謀殺<br />\n無死人不等於無罪<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀仲有<br />\n李家超係受美國OFAC制裁人士<br />\n與非洲惡名昭彰嘅殺人犯 恐怖分子齊名<br />\n用香港法庭嘅講法<br />\n佢並非誠實可靠 所作出嘅論述不應給予任何比重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"正解，唔好比佢個撚樣偷換概念"},{"pid":"281fc43c3cae9b8b1e2b57f24b52697f878d2259","tid":2208170,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T04:32:18.000Z","msg":"佢話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce22f8608efb02485ea611666fe9d2a70d237779","tid":2208170,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"國際通緝犯根本無資格治港"},{"pid":"4886f332e7ffa767bb357db8bfb66f1168352ca6","tid":2208170,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T04:42:23.000Z","msg":"用死人做標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81568f18d6dbb52f29b3e4c30c614ead4fc1227","tid":2208170,"uid":322130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"死左變浮屍當睇唔到，點證明唔係黑警做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadfc8dc84e964c8e62bde29d840e374c44d87cb","tid":2208170,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c98fb7fc00caa2a1836afa8b6dd89ec0c57c47a6","tid":2208170,"uid":1544,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"壓尖沙咀頸死又唔計？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"唔係現場死，所以唔計"},{"pid":"fe076e4b2a0263e573d59a477a27df3396fb2fd7","tid":2208170,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T04:43:45.000Z","msg":"全部都係跳樓同跳海自殺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a